      "title": "Set the function value",
      "content": "Set $C(t)$ equal to $247$.<br/>$$240(53/52)^{t-15}+7=247$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Isolate the exponential part",
      "content": "Subtract $7$ and divide by $240$.<br/>$$(53/52)^{t-15}=1$$"
    },
    {
      "title": "Solve the exponent",
      "content": "The base is not $1$, so the exponent is $0$.<br/>$$t-15=0$$<br/>$$t=15$$<br/>The answer is <strong>15</strong>."
